channel.title: Royalty-Scape [474]
channel.description:
Hey guys, royalty scape is a brand new 474!
Me and a few friends have been working on it awhile, we will be adding pictures very soon! We current have some staff positions open to be obtained by you lucky guys..
We will also be handing out donator rank to a few lucky joiners :)
Current Bugs Needing Fixed: Staff Zone is going to be re-done (ripped it from my friends source) Armadyl Godsword Special needs boosted a little. KBD needs to be reduced in damage. 100% clipping (We currently have 90% clipping as a estimation)
My friend andy will be adding more details and pictures very shortly, if you login fast you'll be able join in on the server screenshots!
http://uppit.com/kh1f8y1gc9cr/RoyaltyScape.jar - Hurry and login and help us take some server screenshots (:
